{"tid":1802743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會要大家幫幫手投票！","createTime":"2019-12-29T16:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T05:31:10.000Z","uid":137716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"af4768143186f3f3e58eafa0cd89349b2b77b667","tid":1802743,"uid":137716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"2019年，香港人一同經歷了將近七個月的民主運動，我們一同為政權的無恥憤怒過、為一眾挺身而出守衛香港的同路人感動過、為我們熱愛的家園努力過、為那些驟然於暴政手上結束的生命痛心過。在今年結束之前，我們希望透過一次全民投票，與大家回憶民主運動中種種深刻的人和事，亦為來年借鑑。一年將盡，但抗暴的戰火仍要繼續點燃，直到成功光復香港！  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK985Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=9ed07ef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a><br />\n大家快d投票，5分鐘搞掂，記得要share埋比屋企人，朋友，長輩一齊投。唔係既話認受性會低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bd8547fff6154299c58740c2077cf77b26555e","tid":1802743,"uid":137716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"投你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f169a3ffa90df2c2316618bfcfcb1a748326ad","tid":1802743,"uid":41161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"投咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d121c9a51868b75994e73f4e8e436ebe0b8bc6df","tid":1802743,"uid":137716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"我投撚左姐姐 妹妹 你呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9d06d277ab34d72d2f4be85614449952b8ab2f","tid":1802743,"uid":137716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f169a3ffa90df2c2316618bfcfcb1a748326ad","tid":1802743,"uid":41161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"投咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2